This is the default shield used by Mecha version `1.x.x`.

### Features

 - Automatic menu navigation
 - Automatic breadcrumb navigation
 - Automatic set the home page view to `article`
 - Comments (requires Comment extension)
 - Page views counter (requires View plugin)
 - Manual post excerpt (requires Excerpt plugin)
 - Formats (requires Type extension)
 - Widgets:
   - Tags (requires Tag extension)
   - Recent Posts
   - Related Posts
   - Recent Comments (requires Comment extension)
   - List (custom)

### Widgets

To create a custom widget, open `aside.php` file then add this code just before the `</aside>` tag:

~~~ .php
<?php static::widget([
    'id' => 'foo-bar', // Optional
    'title' => 'Your Custom Widget Title', // Optional
    'content' => '<p>Your custom widget content.</p>'
]); ?>
~~~

Example widget as advertisement container:

~~~ .php
<?php

$content = <<<HTML

// Remove this line then paste your AD code here!

HTML;

static::widget([
  'title' => 'Advertisement',
  'content' => $content
]);

?>
~~~

Example widget list:

~~~ .php
<?php static::widget('list', [
    'title' => 'My List',
    'list' => [
        'List Item 1',
        'List Item 2',
        'List Item 3',
    ]
]); ?>
~~~

Example widget list as link list:

~~~ .php
<?php static::widget('list', [
    'title' => 'My List',
    'list' => [
        HTML::a('Link 1', 'http://example.com/link-1'),
        HTML::a('Link 2', 'http://example.com/link-2'),
        HTML::a('Link 3', 'http://example.com/link-3'),
    ]
]); ?>
~~~

